          <div class="about-text">
            <h2>About me</h2>

            <p>
              Welcome to my art gallery! My name is Zaryana, and art is one of
              my greatest passions. I create whenever I can, finding inspiration
              in my family, friends, and the everyday moments that often go
              unnoticed. As a mother who works at a hospital, free time can be
              limited, but making art allows me to slow down, reflect, and
              express what matters most to me.
            </p>

            <p>
              I believe art is one of the many ways we can make the world more
              beautiful. It has the power to tell stories, spark emotion, and
              help others see things from a new perspective. Creating art
              motivates me to keep exploring, learning, and sharing my
              creativity with others.
            </p>

            <p>
              In addition to my artwork, I also enjoy sewing and have made many
              handmade stuffed animals for my children. This love for creating
              by hand influences my artistic style and reminds me that
              creativity can take many forms.
